2004-04-11 minimap-0.9.2
------------------------
- TGA datatype 3 support (8bpp grayscale)
- Error dialog if unable to open or process ERF

2004-04-06 minimap-0.9.1
------------------------
- Better handling for unrecognized TGA formats.
- Unrecognized TGA's will show up as reddish tiles by default.
  Uncheck Prefs->Image->Flag bad tile images to make them show up white.

2004-03-28 minimap-0.9.0
------------------------
- Too many things to remember, sorry :)

2004-03-17 minimap-0.2.4
------------------------
- Now handles targa datatype 10 rle encoding
- Now handles non 16x16 tiles
- Splash screen with progress message

2004-03-14 minimap-0.2.3
------------------------
- The area box supports 'extended' style multiselect
- Map windows cleaned up (controls up top and inline)
- Improved module load performance, should be close
  to 0.1.0 performance.

2004-03-14 minimap-0.2.2
------------------------
- Reads configuration from config file
  Linux:   $HOME/.vespucci
  Windows: {launchdir}/vespucci.ini
- Scaling support and UI

2004-03-12 minimap-0.2.1
------------------------
- ActiveState Perl doesn't like Tk::Photo->write, use workaround

2004-03-11 minimap-0.2.0
------------------------
- Resources.pm will load all HAK's associated with a .mod or .nwm
- GFF.pm now returns a ref to an array of strings if the fields is a
  CExoLocString
- Map windows now use Name instead of Resref
- Default base directory chosen based on OS
- Loading a new ERF will eject old ERF resources first
- Maps may be saved
- A per-image combobox offers names based on:
  - ResRef
  - Name
  - Tag
- The combobox allows user input.
- Default name configurable

2004-02-23 minimap-0.1.0
------------------------
Initial release
